en must include the fire and emergency file.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) If all persons consulted express their views before the end of the period referred to in paragraph (2)(b) then the prohibition against determining the application ceases to apply on the day after the date on which their views are received by the regulator.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) The regulator is not required to consult under this regulation where it is satisfied following consideration of the application there are sufficient grounds to reject the application.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Building control approval applications for HRB work or stage of HRB work: decisions"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-7"}], ["7."]}, "—(1) The regulator must grant the building control approval sought in a building control approval application for HRB work or a building control approval application for a stage of HRB work unless the application or any document that accompanied the application—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["does not comply with the requirements of regulation 4 (building control approval applications for HRB work or stage of HRB work) or any direction relating to the application or the document given by the regulator under regulation 59 (electronic submission and directions);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is not sufficiently detailed in any respect to allow the regulator to determine whether the HRB work or the stage of HRB work would contravene any applicable requirement of the building regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["shows the HRB work or the stage of HRB work would contravene any applicable requirement of the building regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-1-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["shows the strategies, policies or procedures in relation to the HRB work or the stage of HRB work (including in relation to controlled changes, mandatory occurrence reporting, competence of persons or sharing of information and co-operation) would contravene, or would be likely to contravene, the requirements of—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-1-d-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulations 18 to 21 and 26 to 29 (changes to documents or persons);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-1-d-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulations 31, 38 and 39 (golden thread etc);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-1-d-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulations 32 to 37 (mandatory occurrence reporting);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-1-d-iv"}], ["(iv)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["Part 2A (dutyholders and competence) of the 2010 Regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) If one or more of the reasons in paragraph (1) applies, the regulator may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["reject the building control approval application for HRB work or the building control approval application for a stage of HRB work, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["with the written consent of the applicant, grant the building control approval sought in the application subject to one or more requirements."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The types of requirement that may be imposed under paragraph (2)(b) include—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a requirement to provide a specified plan or document, or a revised version of a specified plan or document, within a specified period;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a requirement that work does not proceed beyond a specified point until a specified plan or other document, or a revised version of a specified plan or other document, has been given to, and approved by, the regulator."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The regulator must notify the applicant of the outcome of the application (and where the applicant is not the client, also give a copy of the notification to the client) within the period referred to in regulation 5 (building control approval applications for HRB work or stage of HRB work: validity and time limit).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) A notice that the application has been rejected must give the reasons for rejection.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) A notice that the building control approval sought in the application has been granted subject to a requirement must specify the requirement imposed.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) If requested by the applicant, the regulator must provide a paper copy of the notice of building control approval.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where a building control approval application for HRB work or a building control approval application for a stage of HRB work is successful the effect is that from the date of the notice under paragraph (4)—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["building control approval for the HRB work or, as the case may be, building control approval for the stage of HRB work is granted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subject to paragraphs (9) and (10)—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-8-b-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the description of the proposed HRB work or, as the case may be, the description of the proposed stage of HRB work,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-8-b-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the plans of the HRB work or, as the case may be, the plans of the stage of HRB work that accompanied the application, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-8-b-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["each of the other documents that accompanied the application,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["are approved.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Where building control approval has been granted subject to a requirement that a plan or document must be revised, the unrevised plan or document is not approved by paragraph (8)(b).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-10-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["building control approval has been granted subject to a requirement that any plan or document must be revised, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-10-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the plan or document is subsequently revised in accordance with the requirement,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["then that revised plan or document is approved from the date specified in the approval given by the regulator for the revision.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) Where building control approval has been granted subject to a requirement of a type described in paragraph (3)(a), the client must ensure that work does not start before the plan or document is provided.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(12) Where building control approval has been granted subject to a requirement of a type described in paragraph (3)(b)—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-12-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the requirement must set out the points specified in relation to the work and the plans or documents which must be approved for each point;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-7-12-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the client must ensure work to which the requirement relates does not proceed beyond the point specified in the requirement until the approval by the regulator in relation to that plan or document has been received."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(13) If requested by the client, the regulator must provide a paper copy of the approval referred to in paragraph (12)(b).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(14) Where the regulator decides not to approve a plan or document under paragraph (12) if requested the regulator must give the reasons for the decision.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Regulator’s power to require notifications etc for HRB work or stage of HRB work"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-8"}], ["8."]}, "—(1) The regulator may, by notice in writing, require a client—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-8-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to notify the regulator, within a specified period, when a specified point of the HRB work or a specified point of the stage of HRB work has been reached;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-8-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["not to cover up specified work for a specified period."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) In this regulation “", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-specified"}], ["specified"]}, "” means specified by the regulator in the notice referred to in paragraph (1).\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Notice before starting on site and further notice when work is “commenced”"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-9"}], ["9."]}, "—(1) This regulation applies where building control approval for HRB work or building control approval for a stage of HRB work is granted under regulation 7 (building control approval applications for HRB work or stage of HRB work: decisions).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) At least five working days before the day on which the HRB work or the stage of HRB work starts, the client must give a notice to the regulator setting out their intention to start the work and the date that work is to start.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Not more than five working days after the day on which the HRB work is to be regarded as commenced the client must give a notice to that effect to the regulator.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) If the regulator is not satisfied the work is to be regarded as commenced it must give the client a notice to that effect (“rejection notice”) within four weeks of the date the notice under paragraph (3) is given, and the rejection notice must give the reasons for rejection.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where a notice is given under paragraph (3) and the period referred to in paragraph (4) expires without a rejection notice being given, then the work is to be regarded as commenced.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) If the client accepts the rejection notice they may not give a further notice under paragraph (3) unless, having regard to the reasons given by the regulator, they are satisfied the work is to be regarded as commenced.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) The client may appeal to the First-tier Tribunal against the decision of the regulator to reject the notice provided the appeal is made within 21 relevant days beginning with the day after the day on which the regulator gives the rejection notice.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) The First-tier Tribunal may allow an appeal under paragraph (7) only if it is satisfied that the decision appealed against was wrong on one or more of the following grounds—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-9-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that the decision was based on an error of fact;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-9-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that the decision was wrong in law;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-9-8-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that the decision was unreasonable;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-9-8-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that the decision was made without following the procedures set out in the 1984 Act or regulations made under that Act."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Where a notice under paragraph (2) or (3) is given by someone on behalf of the client, the notice must include a statement signed by the client confirming they agree to the notice being given and that the information contained in it is correct.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) The regulator may take such steps, including—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-9-10-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring information;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-9-10-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["laying open of work for inspection,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["as it thinks appropriate to check whether the work is to be regarded as commenced.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) For the purposes of paragraphs (3) to (10) the provisions of regulation 46A (lapse of building control approval: commencement of work) of the 2010 Regulations apply to determine whether work is to be regarded as commenced.\r"]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "part-2-chapter-2"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearChapter"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegChapter"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegChapterNo"}], ["CHAPTER 2"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegChapterTitle"}], ["Existing HRBs"]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitleFirst"}], ["Notification of emergency repairs to existing HRB"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-10"}], ["10."]}, "—(1) Where work to existing HRB consists only of emergency repairs and it is not practicable to comply with regulation 11(1) (building control approval for work to existing HRB) before starting the work, the client must—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-10-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["give a notice to that effect to the regulator, describing the work and the reasons for the urgency as soon as reasonably practicable after the work has started,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-10-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["send a copy of that notice to the responsible person as soon as reasonably practicable after the work has started, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-10-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["submit a regularisation certificate application to the regulator in relation to the work as soon as reasonably practicable after the work is carried out."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) In this regulation—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-emergency-repairs"}], ["emergency repairs"]}, "” means repairs to a building which are necessary to be carried out as a matter of urgency due to the risk to health, safety or welfare of persons in or about the building;\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-responsible-person"}], ["responsible person"]}, "” has the meaning given in article 3 of the Regulatory Reform (Fire Safety) Order 2005.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Building control approval for work to existing HRB"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-11"}], ["11."]}, "—(1) Subject to paragraph (2), before any person starts any work to existing HRB the client in relation to that work (in this Chapter “the applicant”) must—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-11-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["submit an application for building control approval in relation to the work to the regulator (a “building control approval application for work to existing HRB”) in accordance with regulation 12 (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-11-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["be granted building control approval for the work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-11-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["fulfil those requirements, if any, which in accordance with the building control approval must be fulfilled before the work is started, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-11-1-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["notify the regulator of the date on which the work is to start in accordance with regulation 17(2) (notice before starting on site and further notice when work is “commenced”)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) The requirements of this regulation do not apply to work to existing HRB which consists only of—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-11-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["scheme work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-11-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["exempt work, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-11-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["work to which regulation 10 (notification of emergency repairs to existing HRB) applies."]}, "\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Building control approval applications for work to existing HRB"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-12"}], ["12."]}, "—(1) Subject to paragraphs (3) and (4), where a building control approval application for work to existing HRB is required by regulation 11 (building control approval for work to existing HRB), it must be made in writing, signed by the applicant, and must include—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-12-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"