ing control approval application for work to existing HRB the regulator must consult—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-14-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the work is—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-14-1-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["category A work, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-14-1-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["category B work and Part B of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations imposes requirements in relation to the work,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the enforcing authority (within the meaning of article 25 of the Regulatory Reform (Fire Safety) Order 2005(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00016"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 16"}, {"id", "Backf00016"}], ["16"]}, ")) for the building, and\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-14-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where paragraph H4 of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations imposes requirements in relation to the work, the sewerage undertaker for the building."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where the regulator is required to consult a person under this regulation the regulator—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-14-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["must give the person sufficient plans to show whether the work to existing HRB would, if carried out in accordance with those plans, comply with—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP