, ["(5) The regulator is not required to consult under this regulation where it is satisfied following consideration of the application there are sufficient grounds to reject the application.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) In this regulation “category A work” and “category B work” have the meanings given in regulation 12 (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB).\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Building control approval applications for work to existing HRB: decisions"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-15"}], ["15."]}, "—(1) The regulator must grant the building control approval sought in a building control approval application for work to existing HRB unless—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the application or any document that accompanied the application (or is provided under regulation 12(5) (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB))—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["does not comply with the requirements of regulation 12 (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB) or any direction relating to the application or the document given by the regulator under regulation 59 (electronic submission and directions);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["is not sufficiently detailed in any respect to allow the regulator to determine whether the work would contravene any applicable requirement of the building regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["shows that—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-iii-aa"}], ["(aa)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["the proposed work would contravene any applicable requirement of the building regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-iii-bb"}], ["(bb)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["in a case where details are provided under regulation 12(1)(e)(viii)(bb), the work set out in the details would not in the regulator’s opinion amount to 15% of the work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-iv"}], ["(iv)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["shows the strategies, policies or procedures in relation to the work (including in relation to controlled changes, mandatory occurrence reporting, competence of persons or sharing of information and co-operation) would contravene, or would be likely to contravene, the requirements of—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-iv-aa"}], ["(aa)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["regulations 18 to 21 and 26 to 29 (changes to documents or persons);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-iv-bb"}], ["(bb)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["regulations 31, 38 and 39 (golden thread etc);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-iv-cc"}], ["(cc)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["regulations 32 to 37 (mandatory occurrence reporting);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-a-iv-dd"}], ["(dd)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["Part 2A (dutyholders and competence) of the 2010 Regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["when requested pursuant to regulation 12(5) (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB), the applicant failed to provide the document requested."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) If one or more of the reasons in paragraph (1) applies, the regulator may—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["reject the building control approval application for work to existing HRB, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["with the written consent of the applicant, grant the building control approval sought in the application subject to one or more requirements."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The types of requirement that may be imposed under paragraph (2)(b) include—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a requirement to provide a specified plan or document, or a revised version of a specified plan or document, within a specified period;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a requirement that work does not proceed beyond a specified point until a specified plan or other document, or a revised version of a specified plan or other document, has been given to, and approved by, the regulator."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The regulator must notify the applicant of the outcome of the application (and where the applicant is not the client, also give a copy of the notification to the client) within the period referred to in regulation 13 (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB: validity and time limit).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) A notice that the application has been rejected must give the reasons for rejection.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) A notice that the building control approval sought in the application has been granted subject to a requirement must specify the requirement imposed.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) If requested by the applicant, the regulator must provide a paper copy of the notice of building control approval.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where a building control approval application for work to existing HRB is successful the effect is that from the date of the notice under paragraph (4)—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["building control approval for the work to existing HRB is granted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subject to paragraphs (9) and (10)—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-8-b-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the description of the proposed work under regulation 12(1)(e) (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-8-b-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the plans of the work that accompanied the application, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-8-b-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["each of the other documents that accompanied the application and, in accordance with regulation 12(5) (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB), the regulator required to be provided,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["are approved.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Where building control approval has been granted subject to a requirement that a plan or document must be revised, the unrevised plan or document is not approved by paragraph (8)(b).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) Where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-10-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["building control approval has been granted subject to a requirement that any plan or document must be revised, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-10-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the plan or document is revised in accordance with the requirement,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["paragraph (8)(b) applies in relation to the revised plan or document.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) Where building control approval has been granted subject to a requirement of a type described in paragraph (3)(a), the client must ensure that work does not start before the plan or document is provided.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(12) Where building control approval has been granted subject to a requirement of a type described in paragraph (3)(b)—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-12-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the requirement must set out the points specified in relation to the work and the plans or documents which must be approved for each point;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-15-12-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the client must ensure work does not proceed beyond the point specified in a requirement until the approval by the regulator in relation to that plan or document has been received."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(13) If requested by the client, the regulator must provide a paper copy of the approval referred to in paragraph (12)(b).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(14) Where the regulator decides not to approve a plan or document under paragraph (12) if requested the regulator must give the reasons for the decision.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Regulator’s power to require notifications etc for work to existing HRB"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-16"}], ["16."]}, "—(1) The regulator may, by notice in writing, require a client—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-16-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to notify the regulator, within a specified period, when a specified point of the work to existing HRB has been reached;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-16-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["not to cover up specified work for a specified period."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) In this regulation “", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-specified"}], ["specified"]}, "” means specified by the regulator in the notice referred to in paragraph (1).\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Notice before starting on site and further notice when work is “commenced”"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-17"}], ["17."]}, "—(1) This regulation applies where building control approval for work to existing HRB is granted under regulation 15 (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB: decisions).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) At least five working days before the day on which the work to existing HRB starts, the client must give a notice to the regulator setting out their intention to start the work and the date that work is to start.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Not more than five working days after the day on which the work to existing HRB is to be regarded as commenced the client must give a notice to that effect to the regulator.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) If the regulator is not satisfied the work is to be regarded as commenced it must give the client a notice to that effect (“rejection notice”) within four weeks of the date the notice under paragraph (3) is given, and the rejection notice must give the reasons for rejection.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where a notice is given under paragraph (3) and the period referred to in paragraph (4) expires without a rejection notice being given, then the work is to be regarded as commenced.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) If the client accepts the rejection notice they may not give a further notice under paragraph (3) unless, having regard to the reasons given by the regulator, they are satisfied the work is to be regarded as commenced.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) The client may appeal to the First-tier Tribunal against the decision of the regulator to reject the notice provided the appeal is made within 21 relevant days beginning with the day after the day on which the regulator gives the rejection notice.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) The First-tier Tribunal may allow an appeal under paragraph (7) only if it is satisfied that the decision appealed against was wrong on one or more of the following grounds—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-17-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that the decision was based on an error of fact;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-17-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that the decision was wrong in law;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-17-8-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that the decision was unreasonable;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-17-8-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["that the decision was made without following the procedures set out in the 1984 Act or regulations made under that Act."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Where a notice under paragraph (2) or (3) is given by someone on behalf of the client, the notice must include a statement signed by the client confirming they agree to the notice being given and that the information contained in it is correct.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) The regulator may take such steps, including—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-17-10-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["requiring information;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-17-10-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["laying open of work for inspection,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["as it thinks appropriate to check whether the work is to be regarded as commenced.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) For the purposes of paragraphs (3) to (10) the provisions of regulation 46A (lapse of building control approval: commencement of work) of the 2010 Regulations apply to determine whether work is to be regarded as commenced.\r"]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "part-3"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPart"}], []}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegPart"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartNo"}], ["PART 3"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], ["Changes before or during construction"]}]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitleFirst"}], ["Change control"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-18"}], ["18."]}, "—(1) This regulation applies where one or more of the following changes (“controlled change”) is proposed—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a change to any current plans of any work or proposed work or the carrying out of work otherwise than in accordance with the current plans;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a change to any stage of HRB work, including adding or removing a stage;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a change to any strategies, policies or procedures described in any current agreed document."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Before any controlled change can be carried out, the client must ensure—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a record is made of the controlled change in accordance with regulation 19 (change control: record-keeping), and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a revised version of any agreed document affected by the controlled change is produced."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where the controlled change is a notifiable change, the client must notify the regulator in accordance with regulation 20 (change control: notification requirements).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) A notifiable change must not be carried out, and the work to which it relates must not start, until the notification referred to in paragraph (3) has occurred.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where the controlled change is a major change, the client must make an application for building control approval in respect of the change (a “change control application”) to the regulator in accordance with regulation 21 (change control applications).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) A major change must not be carried out, and the work to which it relates must not start, until the change control application is granted.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Paragraph (8) applies where two or more controlled changes are related to the same change to the building work (“related changes”) and at least one of those controlled changes is a major change and at least one is a notifiable change.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where this paragraph applies—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["all the major changes which are related changes may be included in the same change control application,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any notifiable changes which are related changes may also be included in that change control application, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-8-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in relation to any change which is a notifiable change, the requirements of regulation 20 (change control: notification requirements) are satisfied by providing details of the change as part of that application."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Where two or more controlled changes are not related to the same change to the building work they must not be included in the same change control application.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) Paragraph (11) applies where a change control application has been submitted in relation to a proposed change (“the main change”) and it is proposed another controlled change (excluding a change which is only a recordable change) is to be carried out which is consequential on the main change (“a consequential change”) but was not included in an application of the type referred to in paragraph (8).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) Where this paragraph applies—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-11-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a consequential change which is a notifiable change must not be notified in accordance with regulation 20 (change control: notification requirements);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-18-11-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a change control application in relation to a consequential change which is a major change must not be made in accordance with regulation 21 (change control applications),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["until the regulator has notified the client of the outcome of the change control application in relation to the main change.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(12) In this regulation—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-current-agreed-document"}], ["current agreed document"]}, "” means the document that is an agreed document at the time the controlled change is proposed;\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-current-plans"}], ["current plans"]}, "” means the plans that are an agreed document at the time the controlled change is proposed.\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Change control: record-keeping"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-19"}], ["19."]}, "—(1) The principal contractor (or sole contractor) must create and maintain a document for the purposes of recording information in respect of changes to the project (“change control log”).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) A controlled change must be recorded by entering the following information in the change control log—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the name of the individual recording the change,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a description of the proposed change,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["an explanation of the reasons why the change has been proposed,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["whether the change is a recordable change, a notifiable change or a major change,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a list of the name and occupation of each person, if any, whose advice was sought in relation to the proposed change and a summary of any advice provided,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["an assessment of which agreed document is affected by the proposed change and confirmation that a revised version has been produced in accordance with regulation 18(2)(b) (change control), and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-g"}], ["(g)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["an explanation, in relation to the proposed change, of how—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-g-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the HRB work, the stage of HRB work or work to existing HRB will, after the proposed change is carried out, comply with all applicable building regulations, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-g-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the strategies, policies and procedures in any agreed document (including in relation to controlled changes, mandatory occurrence reporting, competence of persons or sharing of information and co-operation) will, after the proposed change is carried out, comply with the requirements of—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-g-ii-aa"}], ["(aa)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["this regulation and regulations 18, 20, 21 and 26 to 29 (changes to documents or persons);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-g-ii-bb"}], ["(bb)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["regulations 31, 38 and 39 (golden thread etc);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-19-2-g-ii-cc"}], ["(cc)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["regulations 32 to 37 (mandatory occurrence reporting);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS 