igner (or sole or lead designer),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-21-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a statement that the application is made under this regulation, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-21-1-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a description of the proposed controlled change."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) The application must be accompanied by—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-21-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["an explanation of the reasons why the change has been proposed,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-21-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a list of the name and occupation of each person, if any, whose advice was sought in relation to the proposed change and a summary of any advice provided,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-21-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the change is to the number of flats or residential rooms, plans showing the number of flats or residential rooms it is proposed the higher-risk building will contain,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-21-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["an assessment of the agreed documents affected by the proposed change,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-21-2-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a compliance explanation in relation to the proposed change, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-21-2-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the application is made by someone on behalf of the client, a statement signed by the client confirming they agree to the application being made and that the information contained in the application is correct,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["and the application must be accompanied by the revised version of the agreed document produced in accordance with regulation 18(2)(b) (change control).\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Change control applications: validity and time limit"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-22"}], ["22."]}, "—(1) Where the regulator receives a change control application which is valid the regulator must—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-22-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["notify the applicant to that effect, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-22-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["determine it within 6 weeks beginning with the date the application is received by the regulator or within such longer period as at any time the regulator and the applicant agree in writing."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where the regulator receives a change control application which is not valid the regulator must notify the applicant to that effect giving reasons (and where the applicant is not the client, also give a copy of the notification to the client).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) A change control application is valid if it complies with regulation 21 (change control applications).\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Change control applications: consultation"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-23"}], ["23."]}, "—(1) Before determining a change control application relating to a controlled change of a kind described in regulation 18(1)(a) (change control), the regulator must consult—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-23-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the enforcing authority (within the meaning of article 25 of the Regulatory Reform (Fire Safety) Order 2005(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00017"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 17"}, {"id", "Backf00017"}], ["17"]}, ")) for the building or proposed building where Part B of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations imposes requirements in relation to the work to which the controlled change relates, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-23-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the sewerage undertaker for the building or proposed building where paragraph H4 of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations imposes requirements in relation to the work to which the controlled change relates."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where the regulator is required to consult a person under this regulation the regulator—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-23-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["must give the person sufficient plans to show whether the work would, if carried out in accordance with those plans, comply with—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-23-2-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["in the case of the enforcing authority, the applicable requirements of Part B (fire safety) of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-23-2-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["in the case of the sewerage undertaker, the requirements of paragraph H4 of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-23-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["must not determine the application until the expiry of a period of 10 working days beginning with the date the consultation starts or such longer period as the regulator and the person consulted agree in writing."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) In relation to the consultation under paragraph (1)(a) the plans given must include the fire and emergency file or, where the work to which the application relates is category B work, the fire safety compliance information.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) If all persons consulted express their views before the end of the period referred to in paragraph (2)(b) then the prohibition against determining the application ceases to apply on the day after the date on which their views are received by the regulator.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) The regulator is not required to consult under this regulation where it is satisfied following consideration of the application there are sufficient grounds to reject the application.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) In this regulation, “", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-category-b-work"}], ["category B