egP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["states the name and address of the client, and where the person is a company, also the company registration number;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["gives details which are sufficient to identify every project of the client which relates to a higher-risk building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-1-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["provides so much of the information referred to in the table in rule 1.6 of the Insolvency (England and Wales) Rules 2016 as is known to them (", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00019"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 19"}, {"id", "Backf00019"}], ["19"]}, ")."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) The circumstances mentioned in paragraph (1) are—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a moratorium under Part A1 of the Insolvency Act 1986(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00020"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 20"}, {"id", "Backf00020"}], ["20"]}, ") has commenced;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a voluntary arrangement for the purposes of Part 1 of the Insolvency Act 1986 has been proposed under that Part of the Act;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a voluntary arrangement for the purposes of Part 8 of the Insolvency Act 1986 has been proposed and has taken effect under that Part of the Act."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Subject to paragraph (5), where a person (“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-p"}], ["P"]}, "”) described in paragraph (4) is appointed in relation to the client then not more than 14 days after the date P is appointed P must give a notice to the regulator which—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["states the name and address of the client in relation to which the appointment relates and gives details which are sufficient to identify every project of the client which relates to a higher-risk building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["identifies the nature of the appointment held by P in relation to the client;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-3-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["states the name, address, telephone number and email address (if any) of P;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-3-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["provides so much of the information referred to in the table in rule 1.6 of the Insolvency (England and Wales) Rules 2016 as is known to them."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The persons referred to in paragraph (3) are—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["an administrator;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["an administrative receiver;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-4-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a receiver appointed by the courts or by a mortgagee;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-4-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a liquidator;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-28-4-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a trustee in bankruptcy."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where under section 178 or 315 of the Insolvency Act 1986 any property in relation to a project is disclaimed, the person disclaiming the property must, within the period of 28 days beginning with the date the disclaimer took effect, give the regulator a copy of the notice of disclaimer under rule 19.2 of the Insolvency (England and Wales) Rules 2016.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) For the purposes of section 35(2) of the 1984 Act (provisions for which offence does not apply) paragraph (3) is prescribed.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) The requirements of this regulation do not apply to a domestic client.\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["New principal contractor or principal designer etc: notification"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-29"}], ["29."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where, at any time after building control approval for HRB work, a stage of HRB work or work to existing HRB is granted the client appoints a principal contractor (or sole contractor) or principal designer (or sole or lead designer).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where paragraph (1) applies, the client must give a notice, signed by the client, to the regulator containing—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address of the person appointed,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a statement that the client—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-2-b-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["has complied with regulation 11E(2)(b) (consideration of past misconduct) of the 2010 Regulations,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-2-b-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["is satisfied in the case of a principal contractor, that the person fulfils the requirements in regulations 11F(1) and (2) and 11H(1) of the 2010 Regulations,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-2-b-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["is satisfied in the case of a principal designer, that the person fulfils the requirements in regulations 11F(1) and (2) and 11G(1) of the 2010 Regulations,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-2-b-iv"}], ["(iv)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["is satisfied in the case of a sole contractor, or sole or lead designer, that the person fulfils the requirements in regulations 11F(1) and (2) of the 2010 Regulations,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in relation to each principal contractor or principal designer, a copy of the record, in respect of the person, that the client created under regulation 11D(8) or (9) (principal designer and principial contractor) of the 2010 Regulations, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a declaration as to the truth of the statement referred to in sub-paragraph (b) and of the record (if any) referred to in sub-paragraph (c)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) On request from the client, the person who was the principal contractor (or sole contractor) or principal designer (or sole or lead designer), as the case may be, before the appointment referred to in paragraph (1) must give the client a statement in writing, signed and dated by them, which sets out—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["their name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the dates of their appointment,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-3-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subject to paragraph (d), a certificate that—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-3-c-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["in the case of a person who was a principal contractor (or sole contractor), that they have fulfilled their duties as a principal contractor under Part 2A (dutyholders and competence) of the 2010 Regulations,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-3-c-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["in the case of a person who was principal designer (or sole or lead designer), that they have fulfilled their duties as a principal designer under Part 2A (dutyholders and competence) of the 2010 Regulations,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-3-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where a person is unable to certify that they have fulfilled their duties, a statement explaining what duties they were unable to fulfil and the reasons for not being able to do so."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The client must ensure the notice under paragraph (2) is accompanied by a copy of a statement provided to them under paragraph (3).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where, at the date a client gives the notice under paragraph (2), the client is unable to obtain the statement under paragraph (3), the notice under paragraph (2) must be accompanied by a statement by the client explaining the steps the client has taken to obtain the statement together with any reasons the person referred to in paragraph (3) has given for not providing the statement.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) The client must give the notice under paragraph (2) together with a copy of the statement referred to in paragraph (3) or, if applicable, a statement referred to in paragraph (5), to the regulator within the period of 14 days beginning with the date of the appointment.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) The client must ensure—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a record is made of the change of principal contractor (or sole contractor) or principal designer (or sole or lead designer) in the change control log, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the construction control plan is revised, in accordance with regulation 18 (change control), to reflect the change."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where the client is a domestic client (DC), the following applies instead of paragraphs (2) to (7)—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["except where the person appointed (PA) is the first person appointed to the role, the person who held the role before PA (“outgoing dutyholder”) must, within five days of the date their appointment ends, give the DC a notice which sets out—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["their name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the date their appointment ended;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-a-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["subject to paragraph (b), a certificate that—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-a-iii-aa"}], ["(aa)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["in the case of a person who was a principal contractor (or sole contractor), that they fulfilled their duties as a principal contractor under Part 2A (dutyholders and competence) of the 2010 Regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-a-iii-bb"}], ["(bb)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["in the case of a person who was principal designer (or sole or lead designer), that they fulfilled their duties as a principal designer under Part 2A (dutyholders and competence) of the 2010 Regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the outgoing dutyholder is unable to certify that they fulfilled their duties, a statement explaining what duties they were unable to fulfil and the reasons for not being able to do so;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["DC must provide the information referred to under sub-paragraph (a) and, as the case may be, (b) to PA on the date of appointment of PA or as soon as practicable after that date;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subject to paragraph (10), PA must give a notice to the regulator which includes—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-d-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the location of the building work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-d-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address of PA and the date of appointment;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-d-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["except where PA is the first person appointed to the role, the name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address of the outgoing dutyholder and the date their appointment ended;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-8-d-iv"}], ["(iv)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["a statement explaining the notice is given on behalf of a domestic client."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) PA must ensure the notice under paragraph (8)(d) is accompanied by a copy of a certificate provided to them under paragraph (8)(a) or a statement provided to them under paragraph (8)(b).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) Where PA has not received the information required to be provided under paragraph (8)(c) by the time the notice under paragraph (8)(d) is to be given, the statement given by PA under paragraph (8)(d)(iv) must also include an explanation to that effect.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) A notice required under paragraph (8)(d) must be given to the regulator within the period of 14 days beginning with the date of the appointment.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(12) PA must ensure—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-12-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a record is made of the change of principal contractor (or sole contractor) or principal designer (or sole or lead designer) in the change control log, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-29-12-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the construction control plan is revised, in accordance with regulation 18 (change control), to reflect the change."]}, "\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Variation of a requirement imposed on a building control approval"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-30"}], ["30."]}, "—(1) In relation to HRB work, a stage of HRB work or work to existing HRB, a client may request, by notice in writing, that the regulator vary a requirement imposed on a building control approval.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) A notice under paragraph (1) must be made in writing, signed by the client, and must include—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-30-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address of the client,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-30-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a statement that the notice is given under this regulation,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-30-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a description of the proposed variation,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-30-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["an explanation of the reasons why the variation is proposed,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-30-2-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a list of the name and occupation of each person, if any, whose advice was sought in relation to the proposed variation and a summary of any advice provided."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where the notice under paragraph (1) is given by someone on behalf of the client, it must include a statement signed by the client confirming they agree to the notice being given and that the information contained in the application is correct.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Where the regulator receives a notice under paragraph (1) the regulator must determine whether to grant the variation within 28 days of receipt of the notice or within such longer period as at any time the regulator and the person giving the notice agree in writing.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where the regulator has not determined whether to grant the variation before the expiry of the period provided for in paragraph (4) then the variation is treated as refused by the regulator.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) Where a requirement is varied the regulator must give the client a notice setting out the requirement as varied.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) If requested by the client, the regulator must provide a paper copy of the notice.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where the regulator does not agree to the variation the regulator must notify the client giving reasons.\r"]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "part-4"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPart"}], []}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegPart"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartNo"}], ["PART 4"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], ["Golden thread, mandatory occurrence reporting, information handover etc"]}]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitleFirst"}], ["Golden thread"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-31"}], ["31."]}, "—(1) The arrangements made by a client under regulation 11A (suitable arrangements to ensure compliance with requirements etc) of the 2010 Regulations must include—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the work is HRB work or a stage of HRB work—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-1-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["arrangements for an electronic facility to be created and maintained by the client (or someone on their behalf) for the purpose of holding the golden thread information;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-1-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["procedures for persons involved with designing or carrying out the work to have access to the facility for the purpose of maintaining the golden thread information in the facility;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the work is work to existing HRB—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-1-b-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["arrangements for an electronic facility which holds the golden thread information to be maintained by the client (or someone on their behalf) for the purpose of updating the golden thread information in relation to the work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-1-b-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["procedures for persons involved with designing or carrying out the work to have access to the facility for the purpose of maintaining the golden thread information in the facility."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) The client must ensure the golden thread information—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is kept in an electronic format,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is capable of being transferred electronically to other persons without the data, information or document in it being lost or corrupted,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is accurate and up to date,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is available in a readable format which is intelligible to the intended readers of the data, and any key needed to understand the data is provided with the data,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-2-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is made available as soon as reasonably practicable following a request from a principal designer (or sole or lead designer) or principal contractor (or sole contractor) to enable them to comply with their requirements under the building regulations,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-2-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is secure from unauthorised access,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-2-g"}], ["(g)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["is only changed in accordance with procedures which record the person who made the change and the date of that change, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-2-h"}], ["(h)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["as far as is reasonably practicable uses language, terminology and definitions which are consistent."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The principal designer (or sole or lead designer) must ensure designs for the building work produced before a building control approval application for HRB work, a stage of HRB work or work to existing HRB is submitted are provided to the client and the client must ensure, before the construction phase begins (or, in the case of a stage of HRB work, that stage begins), the facility referred to in paragraph (1) is updated to include the design.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Where building control approval for HRB work, a stage of HRB work or work to existing HRB is granted the client must ensure, before the construction phase begins (or, in the case of a stage of HRB work, that stage begins), the facility referred to in paragraph (1) includes—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a copy of the fire statement in relation to the higher-risk building or proposed higher-risk building,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the work is HRB work or a stage of HRB work, a copy of the plans and each of the other documents for the proposed higher-risk building which are approved under regulation 7(8)(b) (building control approval applications for HRB work or stage of HRB work: decisions) together with all the evidence recorded to show compliance with the applicable requirements of the building regulations, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-4-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the work is work to existing HRB, a copy of the plans and each of the other documents for the work which are approved under regulation 15(8)(b) (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB: decisions) together with all the evidence recorded to show compliance with the applicable requirements of the building regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where regulation 10 (notification of emergency repairs to existing HRB) applies in relation the work, the client must ensure a copy of the notice required under regulation 10(1)(a) is included in the facility referred to in paragraph (1).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) Where an agreed document is provided or approved under the terms of a requirement imposed on the grant of a building control approval under—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-6-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 7 (building control approval applications for HRB work or stage of HRB work: decisions);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-6-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 15 (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB: decisions);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-6-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 24 (change control applications: decisions),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["the client must ensure the facility referred to in paragraph (1) is updated to include a copy of that agreed document as soon as practicable after the document is provided or approved.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Where a controlled change is proposed the client must ensure a copy of the record required to be made under regulation 18(2)(a) (change control) is included in the facility referred to in paragraph (1) as soon as practicable after the change is recorded and where the proposed change is not carried out the facility referred to in paragraph (1) must be updated with a note to that effect.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where a controlled change is proposed and an agreed document is affected by the change, the client must ensure a copy of the revised version of the document required to be produced under regulation 18(2)(b) (change control) is included in the facility referred to in paragraph (1) as soon as practicable after the revised version is produced and where the proposed change is not carried out the facility referred to in paragraph (1) must be updated with a note to that effect.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Where a notice is given under regulation 29 (new principal contractor or principal designer etc: notification), the client must ensure the facility referred to in paragraph (1) is updated to include a copy of the notice and any statement which accompanied that notice as soon as practicable after the notice is given.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(10) Where a written report is provided to the regulator under regulation 33 (mandatory occurrence reporting: reporting to the regulator), the client must ensure the facility referred to in paragraph (1) is updated to include a copy of that report as soon as practicable after the report is provided.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(11) Where the client proposes to make a completion certificate application or a partial completion certificate application they must ensure the facility referred to in paragraph (1) is updated to include a copy of the proposed application and a copy of each document which it is proposed will accompany the application.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(12) The requirements of this regulation do not apply to work to existing HRB which consists only of—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-12-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["scheme work, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-31-12-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["exempt work."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(13) In this regulation—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-fire-statement"}], ["fire statement"]}, "” means any statement in relation to the higher-risk building or proposed higher-risk building submitted in accordance with article 9A of the Town and Country Planning (Development Management Procedure) (England) Order 2015(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00021"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 21"}, {"id", "Backf00021"}], ["21"]}, ");\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-golden-thread-information"}], ["golden thread information"]}, "” means the information required by this regulation to be included in the facility referred to in paragraph (1), including previous versions of any document which has been updated.\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Mandatory occurrence reporting system"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-32"}], ["32."]}, "—(1) The principal dutyholders(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00022"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 22"}, {"id", "Backf00022"}], ["22"]}, ") must—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-32-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["before the construction phase begins, establish a system which enables as far as is reasonably practicable the prompt reporting of every safety occurrence to the principal dutyholders by reporting persons, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-32-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["maintain the system throughout the construction phase."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) The principal dutyholders must take reasonable steps to ensure each reporting person is provided with adequate instruction and information on the system established by virtue of paragraph (1) and the incidents or situations that should be reported by the reporting person through the system—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-32-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in the case of a designer or contractor, before beginning any work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-32-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in the case of any other person, as soon as reasonably practicable after first entering the site of the work."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The principal contractor (or sole contractor) must ensure an appropriate frequency of inspections of the work for safety occurrences throughout the construction phase.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The principal designer (or sole or lead designer) must ensure an appropriate frequency of inspections of HRB design work for safety occurrences throughout the construction phase.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) The requirements of this regulation do not apply to work to existing HRB which consists only of—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-32-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["exempt work, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-32-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["work to which regulation 10 (notification of emergency repairs to existing HRB) applies."]}, "\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Mandatory occurrence reporting: reporting to the regulator"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-33"}], ["33."]}, "—(1) Where there is a safety occurrence during the construction phase, a principal dutyholder must follow the reporting procedure on becoming aware of the occurrence.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) For the purposes of this regulation, “", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-the-reporting-procedure"}], ["the reporting procedure"]}, "” means—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["notifying the regulator of the safety occurrence by the quickest practicable means without undue delay, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["providing a written report of the occurrence containing the required information (as set out in paragraph (3)) to the regulator within the period of 10 days beginning with the date the principal dutyholder becomes aware of the safety occurrence."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The required information referred to in paragraph (2) is—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the date and time of the safety occurrence;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the address of the site at which the occurrence happened;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-3-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the name, address, telephone number and (if available) an email address of the principal dutyholder making the report;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-3-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the type and details of the occurrence (including the nature of the risk);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-3-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of remedial measures or mitigation carried out."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Information provided by a person under the reporting procedure is not admissible in evidence against that person in criminal proceedings except—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in proceedings for an offence under section 35 of the 1984 Act (offence of contravening building regulations etc) relating to breach of the duty in paragraph (1),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in proceedings for an offence under section 24 of the 2022 Act (provision of false or misleading information to regulator),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-4-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in proceedings for an offence of perverting the course of justice, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-4-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if in the proceedings—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-4-d-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["in giving evidence the person makes a statement inconsistent with the information, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-4-d-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["evidence as to the information that was provided is adduced, or a question relating to it is asked, by or on behalf of the person."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) The requirements of this regulation do not apply to work to existing HRB which consists only of—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["exempt work, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-33-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["work to which regulation 10 (notification of emergency repairs to existing HRB) applies."]}, "\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Mandatory occurrence reporting: defences"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-34"}], ["34."]}, "  Where a principal dutyholder has committed an offence under section 35 of the 1984 Act of contravening these Regulations by failing to follow the reporting procedure in relation to a safety occurrence as required by regulation 33 (mandatory occurrence reporting: reporting to the regulator), it is a defence for the principal dutyholder if it reasonably believed that the other principal dutyholder had—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-34-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["already notified the regulator of the safety occurrence under regulation 33, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-34-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["already provided the regulator with a written report of the safety occurrence under regulation 33."]}, "\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Mandatory occurrence reporting: definitions"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-35"}], ["35."]}, "  In regulations 32 to 34—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-construction-phase"}], ["construction phase"]}, "” means the period of time beginning when the HRB work, a stage of HRB work or work to existing HRB starts and ending when the work is completed;\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-hrb-design-work"}], ["HRB design work"]}, "” means design of any HRB work, stage of HRB work or work to existing HRB;\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-principal-dutyholders"}], ["principal dutyholders"]}, "” means the principal contractor (or sole contractor) and the principal designer (or sole or lead designer);\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-reporting-person"}], ["reporting person"]}, "” means—\r"]}, {"div", [], [{"div", [{"class", "LegAlphaList"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(a)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["any designer (including the principal designer),\r"]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(b)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["any contractor (including the principal contractor), and\r"]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(c)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["any other person who is a periodic visitor on the site of work;\r"]}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-safety-occurrence"}], ["safety occurrence"]}, "” means—\r"]}, {"div", [], [{"div", [{"class", "LegAlphaList"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(a)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["in relation to a design, an aspect of the design relating to the structural integrity or fire safety of a higher-risk building that would, if built, meet the risk condition;\r"]}]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegListItem"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegLevel4No LegListItemNo"}], ["(b)"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel4"}], ["otherwise, an incident or situation relating to the structural integrity or fire safety of a higher-risk building that meets the risk condition.\r"]}]}]}]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) In the definition of “safety occurrence”, the “risk condition” is that use of the building in question without the incident or situation being remedied would be likely to present a risk of a significant number of deaths, or serious injury to a significant number of people.\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Mandatory occurrence reporting: regulator’s annual report"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-36"}], ["36."]}, "  Regulation 33(1) (mandatory occurrence reporting: reporting to the regulator) is prescribed for the purposes of section 19(2)(b) of the 2022 Act.\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Mandatory occurrence reporting: client duty on appointment of principal contractor or principal designer"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-37"}], ["37."]}, "  Where, in relation to HRB work, a stage of HRB work or work to existing HRB, the client appoints a principal contractor (or sole contractor) or principal designer (or sole or lead designer), then the client must take all reasonable steps to satisfy itself that the person appointed is able to fulfil the requirements in regulations 32 (mandatory occurrence reporting system) and 33 (mandatory occurrence reporting: reporting to the regulator).\r"]}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Handover of information on completion etc"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "regulation-38"}], ["38."]}, "—(1) The client for HRB work, a stage of HRB work or work to existing HRB must give—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-38-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the BFLO information; and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "regulation-38-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the specified golden thread information,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["to the relevant person no later than the date the work is completed, or where regulation 45 (partial completion certificates) applies no later than the date the part of the building is to be occupied.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) The golden thread information given under paragraph (1) must be provided in such a way as to retain the filing structure in which it was kept, including each index, key or other information logically associated with it and in a format which enables the relevant person to read, keep and update the information.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) The relevant person must give the client a notice acknowledging receipt of the specified golden thread information which confirms—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFi