, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in a case where full plans have been deposited—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-3-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations do not apply to that work, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-3-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the 2010 Regulations continue to apply to that work, including the amendments made to the 2010 Regulations by the Building Regulations etc. (Amendment) (England) Regulations 2023, but subject to Part 4 (transitional, supplementary and saving provisions) of the Building Regulations etc. (Amendment) (England) Regulations 2023;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in a case where an initial notice has been given—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-3-b-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations do not apply to that work, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-3-b-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the 2010 Regulations and the Building (Approved Inspectors etc.) Regulations 2010 continue to apply to the work, including the amendments made to those Regulations by the Building Regulations etc. (Amendment) (England) Regulations 2023 and the Building (Approved Inspectors etc. and Review of Decisions) (England) Regulations 2023 but subject to Part 4 (transitional, supplementary and saving provisions) of the Building Regulations etc. (Amendment) (England) Regulations 2023 and Part 4 (transitional, supplementary and saving provisions) of the Building (Approved Inspectors etc. and Review of Decisions) (England) Regulations 2023."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) In addition to the continuing application of the provisions referred to in sub-paragraph (3), not more than five working days after the day on which the work is to be regarded as sufficiently progressed the person carrying out the work must give a notice to that effect to the local authority and where sub-paragraph (1)(a) applies in relation to the work, give a copy of the notice to the approved inspector.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Sub-paragraphs (1) to (4) cease to apply in relation to the work where before 6th April 2024—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the approval for the work lapses by virtue of section 32 of the 1984 Act (as that provision had effect immediately before 1st October 2023), or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the initial notice for the work, or the part of that notice which relates to the higher-risk building, is cancelled under section 52(5) of the 1984 Act (as that provision had effect immediately before 1st October 2023),"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2Text"}], ["and paragraph 3 applies instead to the work.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) For the purposes of this paragraph work is to be regarded as sufficiently progressed—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-6-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the building work consists of the construction of a higher-risk building, when the pouring of concrete for—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-6-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the permanent placement of the trench, pad or raft foundations, or"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-6-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the permanent placement of piling,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["for that building has started;\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-6-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the building work consists of work to an existing building, when that work has started;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-1-6-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the building work consists of a material change of use of a building, when work to effect that change of use has started."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Where the work consists of work in relation to more than one higher-risk building then sub-paragraph (4) applies to each building separately.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["From October 2023: cases where full plans are rejected"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2"}], ["2."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where, in relation to work to a particular building, full plans were deposited with a local authority before 1st October 2023 and in accordance with any provision of Part 1 of the 1984 Act or a local enactment the local authority has rejected those plans on or after that date (“the rejection date”).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where this paragraph applies then with effect from the rejection date the regulator, and not the local authority for the area, is the building control authority in relation to the higher-risk building and accordingly—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the duties and functions of the regulator under section 91 of the 1984 Act apply in relation to the higher-risk building or any proposed higher-risk building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations apply to any HRB work or work to existing HRB from the rejection date with the modifications provided in this paragraph except that regulation 47 (regularisation) does not apply in relation to any work carried out before the rejection date and accordingly any reference to a regularisation certificate in Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations is to be ignored, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the 2010 Regulations, to the extent they apply to higher-risk buildings, apply to any of the work from the rejection date."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Within 10 working days of the rejection date the person intending to carry out the work must give a notice to the regulator setting out—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address of the person intending to carry out the work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of the work to be carried out;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-3-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of any existing building on the site, including the height of any existing building, the number of storeys contained in it and the use of each storey (regulations 5 and 6 of the Higher-Risk Buildings (Descriptions and Supplementary Provisions) Regulations 2023(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00041"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 41"}, {"id", "Backf00041"}], ["41"]}, ") have effect in determining the height and the number of storeys in a building);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-3-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of the intended use of the higher-risk building, including the intended use of each storey;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-3-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the height of the higher-risk building as determined in accordance with regulation 5 of the Higher-Risk Buildings (Descriptions and Supplementary Provisions) Regulations 2023;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-3-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the number of storeys in the higher-risk building as determined in accordance with regulation 6 of the Higher-Risk Buildings (Descriptions and Supplementary Provisions) Regulations 2023;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-3-g"}], ["(g)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where the work is HRB work or is work to existing HRB which changes the number of residential or commercial units in the building, the proposed number of flats, number of residential rooms and number of commercial units to be contained in the higher-risk building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-2-3-h"}], ["(h)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of the work which has been carried out together with a summary of the inspections undertaken by the local authority in relation to the work."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Where any work was carried out before the rejection date the person who carried out the work or the owner must comply with any notice from the regulator requiring them within a reasonable time to cut into, lay open or pull down so much of the work as prevents the regulator from ascertaining whether the work contravenes any requirement of the building regulations.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Where any work was carried out before the rejection date (“the HRB project”) and on or after that date a building control approval application for HRB work or a building control approval application for work to existing HRB is submitted to the regulator in respect of the HRB project, then in addition to the requirements of regulation 4 the person who carried out the work must provide the regulator with such plans as are necessary to show the work already carried out complies with all applicable requirements of the building regulations.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["October 2023 to April 2024: cases where building control approval lapses before 6th April 2024"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-3"}], ["3."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where, by virtue of paragraph 1(5)(a) or (b), paragraph 1(1) to (4) ceases to apply in relation to work.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where this paragraph applies then with effect from the date paragraph 1(1) to (4) ceases to apply in relation to the work (“the cessation date”) the regulator, and not the local authority for the area, is the building control authority in relation to the higher-risk building and accordingly—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-3-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the duties and functions of the regulator under section 91 of the 1984 Act apply in relation to the higher-risk building or any proposed higher-risk building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-3-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["these Regulations apply to any of the work from the cessation date, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-3-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the 2010 Regulations, to the extent they apply to higher-risk buildings, apply to any of the work from the cessation date."]}, "\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["October 2023 to April 2024: cases of not sufficiently progressed work where an initial notice is cancelled before 6th April 2024"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4"}], ["4."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the initial notice for the work, or the part of that notice which relates to the higher-risk building, ceases to be in force by virtue of any provision of Part 2 of the 1984 Act (except section 52(5)) on a date before 6th April 2024 (“the cancellation date”), and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a notice under paragraph 1(4) (notice that work had sufficiently progressed) in relation to that work was not received by a local authority before the cancellation date."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where this paragraph applies—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if a plans certificate or final certificate relating to the work (or any part of the work) has been accepted before the cancellation date then with effect from that date the certificate ceases to have effect;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["accordingly Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations apply to the work from the cancellation date with the modifications provided for in paragraph (8);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subject to paragraph (d), the 2010 Regulations, to the extent they apply to higher-risk buildings, apply to any of the work from the cancellation date;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 11(3) of the 2010 Regulations does not apply and accordingly the regulator may exercise the power in section 8(3A) of the 1984 Act(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00042"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 42"}, {"id", "Backf00042"}], ["42"]}, ") to dispense with or relax any requirement of the 2010 Regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where this paragraph applies then with effect from the cancellation date the regulator, and not the local authority for the area, is the building control authority in relation to the higher-risk building and accordingly the duties and functions of the regulator under section 91 of the 1984 Act apply in relation to the work to the higher-risk building (but not in relation to any other work specified in the initial notice).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Where this paragraph applies, not more than five working days after the cancellation date the person which was shown on the initial notice as the approved inspector must—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["give a notice to the person intending to carry out the work explaining the initial notice, or such part of the initial notice which applies to the higher-risk building, is no longer in force and the effect of sub-paragraphs (2), (3) and (5), and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["give a copy of the notice to the local authority."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Within 10 working days of the cancellation date the person intending to carry out the work must give a notice to the regulator setting out—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["their name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the location of the building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-5-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of the work to be carried out;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-5-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the height of the higher-risk building as determined in accordance with regulation 5 of the Higher-Risk Buildings (Descriptions and Supplementary Provisions) Regulations 2023;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-5-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the number of storeys in the higher-risk building as determined in accordance with regulation 6 of the Higher-Risk Buildings (Descriptions and Supplementary Provisions) Regulations 2023, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-5-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a description of any work which was carried out before the cancellation date (including details of the work in relation to which a final certificate was given and not rejected) and details of any inspections undertaken by the approved inspector in relation to that work."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) With effect from the cancellation date no further building work in relation to the work described in the initial notice (“HRB project”) may be carried out until the date when the person intending to carry out building work has received confirmation in writing from the regulator that an application for building control approval made to the regulator in relation to that work is valid (“validation date”).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) Where any building work was carried out before the cancellation date then—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the person who carried out the work or the owner must comply with any notice from the regulator requiring them within a reasonable time to cut into, lay open or pull down so much of the work as prevents the regulator from ascertaining whether the work contravenes any requirement of the building regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in addition to the other documents which are required to accompany the application for building control approval, the person must provide the regulator with such plans as are necessary to show the work already carried out complies with all applicable requirements of the building regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where the application for building control approval in relation to the HRB project is rejected by the regulator then with effect from the date the rejection is notified to the applicant (“rejection date”) no further building work in relation to the HRB project may be carried out until a building control approval is granted in relation to the building.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations have effect in relation to the HRB project—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-9-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["from the cancellation date as if—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-9-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulation 5(1)(b) (building control applications: for HRB work or stage of HRB work: validity and time limit) and regulation 13(1)(b) (building control applications: for work to existing HRB: validity and time limit) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-9-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["in relation to any change control which is proposed or occurs between the cancellation date and the date application for building control approval is determined by the regulator, Part 3 (change control) required the change to be recordable in the change control log;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-9-a-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulation 47 (regularisation) does not apply in relation to any work carried out before the cancellation date and accordingly any reference to a regularisation certificate in Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations in relation to such work is to be ignored;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-9-a-iv"}], ["(iv)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulations 50 to 56 (section 30A applications) did not apply in relation to the application for building control approval for the HRB project, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-4-9-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["additionally, from the validation date until the rejection date, as if regulation 3 did not prevent work in the HRB project to be started before an application for building control approval for the work is submitted."]}, "\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["October 2023 to April 2024: cases of sufficiently progressed work where an initial notice is cancelled before 6th April 2024"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5"}], ["5."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a notice under paragraph 1(4) (notice that work had sufficiently progressed) in relation to that work was received by a local authority before 6th April 2024, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the initial notice for the work, or the part of that notice which relates to the higher-risk building, ceases to be in force by virtue of any provision of Part 2 of the 1984 Act on a date before 6th April 2024 (“the cancellation date”)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where this paragraph applies—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if a final certificate relating to the work (or any part of the work which relates to the higher-risk building) has been accepted before the cancellation date then with effect from that date the function of enforcing building regulations that is conferred on the regulator by section 91(3) of the 1984 Act is not exercisable in relation to that work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if a plans certificate relating to the work (or any part of the work which relates to the higher-risk building) has been accepted before the cancellation date then with effect from the notice date the certificate ceases to have effect;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["accordingly Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations apply to the work from the cancellation date with the modifications provided for in paragraph (9);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subject to paragraph (e), the 2010 Regulations, to the extent they apply to higher-risk buildings, apply to any of the work from the cancellation date;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-2-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 11(3) of the 2010 Regulations does not apply and accordingly the regulator may exercise the power in section 8(3A) of the 1984 Act to dispense with or relax any requirement of the 2010 Regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where this paragraph applies then with effect from the cancellation date the regulator, and not the local authority for the area, is the building control authority in relation to the higher-risk building and accordingly the duties and functions of the regulator under section 91 of the 1984 Act apply in relation to the work to the higher-risk building (but not in relation to any other work specified in the initial notice).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) Where this paragraph applies, not more than five working days after the cancellation date the person which was shown on the initial notice as the approved inspector must—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["give a notice to the person intending to carry out the work explaining the initial notice, or such part of the initial notice which applies to the higher-risk building, is no longer in force and the effect of sub-paragraphs (2), (3) and (5), and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["give a copy of the notice to the local authority."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) Within 10 working days of the cancellation date the person intending to carry out the work must give a notice to the regulator setting out—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-5-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the information referred to in paragraph 4(5), and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-5-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in relation to any work for which a final certificate was given and not rejected, a description of the work covered by the final certificate."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) With effect from the cancellation date no further building work in relation to the work described in the initial notice (“HRB project”) may be carried out until the date when the person intending to carry out building work has submitted an application for building control approval for HRB work or an application for building control approval for work to existing HRB in relation to the work and received confirmation in writing from the regulator that an application for building control approval made to the regulator in relation to that work is valid (“validation date”).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) In relation to building work carried out before the cancellation date then—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the person who carried out the work or the owner must comply with any notice from the regulator requiring them within a reasonable time to cut into, lay open or pull down so much of the work as prevents the regulator from ascertaining whether the work contravenes any requirement of the building regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in addition to the other documents which are required to accompany the application for building control approval, the person must provide the regulator with such plans as are necessary to show the work already carried out complies with all applicable requirements of the building regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where the application for building control approval in relation to the HRB project is rejected by the regulator then with effect from the date the rejection is notified to the applicant (“rejection date”) no further building work in relation to the HRB project may be carried out until a building control approval is granted in relation to the building.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations have effect in relation to the work as if—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in Part 2—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["in relation to any work for which a final certificate was previously given before the cancellation date and not rejected—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-a-i-aa"}], ["(aa)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["paragraphs (1)(e)(viii), (2)(b) and (3) of regulation 4 (building control approval applications for HRB work or stage of HRB work) and paragraphs (1)(e)(viii), (2)(c) and (5) of regulation 12 (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB) were omitted,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-a-i-bb"}], ["(bb)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["in addition to the requirements of regulation 4 and, as the case may be, regulation 12, the person which carried out the work must provide the regulator with such plans as are necessary to show the work already carried out complies with all applicable requirements of the building regulations, together with a copy of the final certificate;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-a-i-cc"}], ["(cc)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["regulation 5(1)(b) (building control applications: for HRB work or stage of HRB work: validity and time limit) and regulation 13(1)(b) (building control applications: for work to existing HRB: validity and time limit) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["in relation to any other work in the HRB project—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-a-ii-aa"}], ["(aa)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["paragraphs (iii) to (viii) of regulation 4(2)(b) (building control approval applications for HRB work or stage of HRB work) and paragraphs (ii) to (vi) of regulation 12(2)(c) and (5) (building control approval applications for work to existing HRB) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-a-ii-bb"}], ["(bb)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["regulation 5(1)(b) (building control applications: for HRB work or stage of HRB work: validity and time limit) and regulation 13(1)(b) (building control applications: for work to existing HRB: validity and time limit) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulations 18 to 26 (change control) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["paragraphs (2)(b), (6)(b) and (8)(c) of regulation 27 (new client etc) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any references to golden thread information in regulation 27 were references to fire safety information;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["paragraph (7) of regulation 29 (new principal contractor or principal designer) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 31 (golden thread) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-g"}], ["(g)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulations 32 to 37 (mandatory occurrence reporting) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-h"}], ["(h)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any references to golden thread information in regulation 38 were references to fire safety information;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in Part 5 (completion certificates), in relation to any work (including any work carried out before the cancellation date which is included in a completion certificate application)—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-i-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["any references to “completion certificate” were references to “transfer and completion certificate”;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-i-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["any references to “partial completion certificate” were references to “transfer and partial completion certificate”;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-i-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["paragraph (2)(d) of regulation 40 (completion certificate applications) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-i-iv"}], ["(iv)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["paragraph (3)(c) of regulation 45 (partial completion certificates) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-j"}], ["(j)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any reference in regulations 40(1)(f) (completion certificate applications), 44(1)(c) (completion certificate applications: decisions) and 45(2)(h) and (10)(c) (partial completion certificates) to providing information to the relevant person in accordance with regulation 38 (handover of information on completion etc) were a reference to providing fire safety information to the relevant person;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-k"}], ["(k)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any reference in regulations 4, 6, 12 and 42 to a “fire and emergency file” were a reference to a document setting out the fire safety design principles, concepts and standards applied to the development including sufficient plans to show how the work would comply with Part B (fire safety) of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations in relation to the higher-risk building or proposed higher-risk building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-l"}], ["(l)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 46 (inspections etc) were omitted in relation to any work described in a final certificate;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-m"}], ["(m)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 47 (regularisation) were omitted in relation to any work carried out before the cancellation date and accordingly any reference to a regularisation certificate in Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations is to be ignored in relation to that work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-n"}], ["(n)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in regulations 48 (review of regulator’s decisions), 50 (section 30A prescribed applications) and 51 (section 30A applications: procedure)—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-n-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["any reference to completion certificate application were a reference to an application for a transfer and completion certificate, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-n-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["any reference to partial completion certificate application were a reference to an application for a transfer and partial completion certificate;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-5-9-o"}], ["(o)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulations 50 to 56 (section 30A applications) were omitted in relation to the application for building control approval for the HRB project."]}, "\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["From April 2024: local authority to notify regulator where work has not sufficiently progressed"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6"}], ["6."]}, "—(1) No later than 6th March 2024, each local authority must give the regulator a notice stating in respect of each relevant building for which it has not by that date received a notice under paragraph 1(4)—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the name and address of the building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address of the person carrying out the work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of the intended use of the higher-risk building, including the intended use of each storey;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the proposed height of the higher-risk building as determined in accordance with regulation 5 of the Higher-Risk Buildings (Descriptions and Supplementary Provisions) Regulations 2023(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00043"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 43"}, {"id", "Backf00043"}], ["43"]}, ");"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the proposed number of storeys in the higher-risk building as determined in accordance with regulation 6 of the Higher-Risk Buildings (Descriptions and Supplementary Provisions) Regulations 2023;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the proposed number of flats, number of residential rooms and number of commercial units proposed to be contained in the higher-risk building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-g"}], ["(g)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the provision to be made for the drainage of the building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-h"}], ["(h)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where paragraph H4 of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations imposes a requirement, the precautions to be taken in the building over a drain, sewer or disposal main to comply with the requirements of that paragraph;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the steps to be taken to comply with any local enactment that applies;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-6-1-j"}], ["(j)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of the work which has been carried out together with a summary of the inspections undertaken by the local authority in relation to the work."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) In this paragraph a “relevant building” is a building in relation to which paragraph 1(1)(b) applies.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["From April 2024: cases where work is to be regarded as sufficiently progressed"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7"}], ["7."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a notice under paragraph 1(4) (notice that work had sufficiently progressed) in relation to work to that building was received by a local authority before 6th April 2024, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in any case where an initial notice was given in relation to the work, the approved inspector which gave the initial notice has become a registered building control approver before 6th April 2024."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where this paragraph applies, with effect from 6th April 2024—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in a case where full plans have been deposited—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7-2-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations continue not to apply to that work, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7-2-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the 2010 Regulations continue to apply to the work but subject to Part 4 (transitional, supplementary and saving provisions) of the Building Regulations etc. (Amendment) (England) Regulations 2023;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["in a case where an initial notice was given in relation to the work by an approved inspector then for so long as the initial notice continues in force—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7-2-b-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the initial notice given by the approved inspector is treated as if it were given instead by that person in their capacity as a registered building control approver,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7-2-b-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations continue not to apply to that work, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-7-2-b-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the 2010 Regulations and the Building (Approved Inspectors etc.) Regulations 2010 continue to apply to the work, but subject to Part 4 (transitional, supplementary and saving provisions) of the Building Regulations etc. (Amendment) (England) Regulations 2023 and Part 4 (transitional, supplementary and saving provisions) of the Building (Approved Inspectors etc. and Review of Decisions) (England) Regulations 2023."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where this paragraph applies then with effect from 6th April 2024 the local authority for the area, and not the regulator, continues to be the building control authority in relation to the higher-risk building and accordingly the duties and functions of local authorities under section 91 of the 1984 Act continue to apply in relation to the work.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["From April 2024: cases of work not sufficiently progressed with an initial notice"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-8"}], ["8."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where, in relation to work to a particular building, paragraph 1 applies in respect of work for which an initial notice was in force, but a notice under paragraph 1(4) (notice that work had sufficiently progressed) was not received by a local authority in relation to the building before 6th April 2024.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where this paragraph applies—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-8-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["for the purposes of section 47(4)(b)(ii) of the 1984 Act the initial notice, or such part of the initial notice which applies to the higher-risk building, ceases to be in force with effect from 6th April 2024;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-8-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if a plans certificate or final certificate relating to the work (or any part of the work) has been accepted before 6th April 2024 then with effect from that date the certificate ceases to have effect;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-8-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subject to paragraph (d), the 2010 Regulations, to the extent they apply to higher-risk buildings, apply to any of the work from that date;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-8-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 11(3) of the 2010 Regulations does not apply and accordingly the regulator may exercise the power in section 8(3A) of the 1984 Act to dispense with or relax any requirement of the 2010 Regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where this paragraph applies, with effect from 6th April 2024 the regulator, and not the local authority for the area, is the building control authority in relation to the higher-risk building and accordingly the duties and functions of the regulator under section 91 of the 1984 Act apply in relation to the work to the higher-risk building (but not in relation to any other work specified in the initial notice).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The provisions of paragraph 4(4) to (9) also apply but as if any reference to the cancellation date were a reference to 6th April 2024.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["From April 2024: cases of work not sufficiently progressed with full plans"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9"}], ["9."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where in relation to work to a particular building paragraph 1 applies in respect of work for which full plans were deposited but a notice under paragraph 1(4) (notice that work had sufficiently progressed) was not received by a local authority in relation to the building before 6th April 2024.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where this paragraph applies, with effect from 6th April 2024 the regulator, and not the local authority for the area, is the building control authority in relation to the higher-risk building and accordingly the duties and functions of the regulator under section 91 of the 1984 Act apply in relation to the work to the higher-risk building (but not in relation to any other work specified in the full plans).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where this paragraph applies the person intending to carry out the work must, within 4 weeks beginning with 6th April 2024, give to the regulator a notice setting out—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the name and address of the building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the name, address, telephone number and (if available) email address of the client, the principal contractor (or sole contractor) and the principal designer (or sole or lead designer);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of the work to be carried out;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of the intended use of the higher-risk building, including the intended use of each storey;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the proposed height of the higher-risk building as determined in accordance with regulation 5 of the Higher-Risk Buildings (Descriptions and Supplementary Provisions) Regulations 2023;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the proposed number of storeys in the higher-risk building as determined in accordance with regulation 6 of the Higher-Risk Buildings (Descriptions and Supplementary Provisions) Regulations 2023;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-g"}], ["(g)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the proposed number of flats, number of residential rooms and number of commercial units to be contained in the higher-risk building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-h"}], ["(h)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the provision to be made for the drainage of the building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where paragraph H4 of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations imposes a requirement, the precautions to be taken in the building over a drain, sewer or disposal main to comply with the requirements of that paragraph;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-j"}], ["(j)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the steps to be taken to comply with any local enactment that applies;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-3-k"}], ["(k)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["details of the work which has been carried out together with a summary of the inspections undertaken by the local authority in relation to the work."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The notice under sub-paragraph (3) must be accompanied by—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a plan to a scale of not less than 1:1250 showing—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the size and position of the proposed building and its relationship to adjoining boundaries;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-a-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the boundaries of the curtilage of the building, and the size, position and use of every other building or proposed building within the curtilage;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-a-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["the width and position of any street on or within the boundaries of the curtilage of the building;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["where work has started, a copy of the notice given to the local authority under regulation 16(1) (commencement notice) of the 2010 Regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["such other documents or plans which were provided to the local authority by the person intending to carry out the work for the purpose of demonstrating the compliance of the work or the proposed work with applicable requirements of the building regulations;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a statement setting out—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-d-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["any conditions imposed on the full plans;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-d-ii"}], ["(ii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["any changes (including any conditions related to the changes), agreed with the local authority, to the full plans;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-d-iii"}], ["(iii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["any work carried out otherwise than in accordance with the full plans (including otherwise than in accordance with any condition impose on the plans);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["copy of any report produced by the local authority in relation to each inspection of the work together with a copy of any notes and photographs relating to the inspections;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-4-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a statement setting out details of any enforcement action taken by the local authority in relation to the work."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(5) The person intending to carry out the work must give a copy of the notice to the local authority.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(6) Where this paragraph applies, with effect from 6th April 2024—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the 2010 Regulations continue to apply to the work, but subject to—"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-a-i"}], ["(i)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["Part 4 (transitional, supplementary and saving provisions) of the Building Regulations etc. (Amendment) (England) Regulations 2023;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-a-ii"}], [