]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP5Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP5No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-viii-bb"}], ["(bb)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP5Text"}], ["before a completion certificate application or a partial completion certificate application is submitted,"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["whichever occurs first;\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-ix"}], ["(ix)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulation 32 (mandatory occurrence reporting system), but as if the reference to establishing the system before the construction phase begins were a reference to establishing it within 10 days beginning with 6th April 2024;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-x"}], ["(x)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulations 33 to 37 (mandatory occurrence reporting) but as if any reference to an agreed document is to be treated as a reference to the full plans;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-xi"}], ["(xi)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulations 38 and 39 (handover of information on completion etc);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-xii"}], ["(xii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulation 40 (completion certificate applications) but as if paragraphs (i), (ii) and (iii) of paragraph (2)(d) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-xiii"}], ["(xiii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulations 41 to 44 (completion certificates etc);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-xiv"}], ["(xiv)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulation 45 (partial completion certificate applications) but as if paragraphs (i), (ii) and (iii) of paragraph (3)(c) were omitted;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-xv"}], ["(xv)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulation 46 (inspections etc);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-xvi"}], ["(xvi)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulations 48 to 56 (reviews and appeals etc) but only to the extent those provisions apply in relation to a change control application or completion certificate application or a partial completion certificate application;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-xvii"}], ["(xvii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulation 58 (requirement for completion certificate before occupation);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP4Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP4No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-b-xviii"}], ["(xviii)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP4Text"}], ["regulation 59 (electronic submission and directions);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-6-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["any reference in regulations 23, 26, 40, 42 and 45 to a “fire and emergency file” were a reference to a document setting out the fire safety design principles, concepts and standards applied to the development including sufficient plans to show how the work would comply with Part B (fire safety) of Schedule 1 to the 2010 Regulations in relation to the higher-risk building or proposed higher-risk building."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(7) The 2010 Regulations have effect with the following modifications—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-7-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["as if any reference in any provision to a local authority, however so expressed, were a reference to the regulator;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-7-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["as if regulations 16(3) to (5), 17, 17A, 18, 18A, 18B, 38, 39, 40, 40A and 40B of the 2010 Regulations were omitted."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(8) Where the regulator receives any document under sub-paragraph (6) it may, by notice in writing, require the client—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-8-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to provide further information specified in the notice by the time specified in the notice;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-9-8-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["to take such steps (including tests) as are specified in the notice by the time specified in the notice to demonstrate the work will comply with all applicable requirements of the building regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(9) Where a notice is given to the client under sub-paragraph (8), that person must not start or, as the case may be, continue the work to which the notice relates for a period of 10 days beginning on the day after the day on which the notice is received.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["From April 2024: cases where work has sufficiently progressed but approved inspector is not a registered building control approver"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-10"}], ["10."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-10-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["paragraph 1 applies in relation to a particular building in respect of work for which an initial notice was in force on 6th April 2024 but the approved inspector which gave the notice was not a registered building control approver on that date, and"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-10-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a notice under paragraph 1(4) (notice that work had sufficiently progressed) in relation to that work was received by a local authority before 6th April 2024."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where this paragraph applies—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-10-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["for the purposes of section 47(4)(b)(ii) of the 1984 Act the initial notice or, such part of the notice which relates to the higher-risk building, ceases to be in force with effect from 6th April 2024;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-10-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if a final certificate relating to the work (or any part of the work which relates to the higher-risk building) has been accepted before 6th April 2024 then with effect from the notice date the function of enforcing building regulations that is conferred on the regulator by section 91(3) of the 1984 Act is not exercisable in relation to that work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-10-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if a plans certificate relating to the work (or any part of the work which relates to the higher-risk building) has been accepted before 6th April 2024 then with effect from the notice date the certificate ceases to have effect;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-10-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["accordingly Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations apply to the work from 6th April 2024 with the modifications provided for in paragraph 5(9) (as applied by paragraph (4));"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-10-2-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subject to paragraph (f), the 2010 Regulations, to the extent they apply to higher-risk buildings, apply to any of the work from that date;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-10-2-f"}], ["(f)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 11(3) of the 2010 Regulations does not apply and accordingly the regulator may exercise the power in section 8(3A) of the 1984 Act to dispense with or relax any requirement of the 2010 Regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where this paragraph applies, with effect from 6th April 2024 the regulator, and not the local authority for the area, is the building control authority in relation to the higher-risk building and accordingly the duties and functions of the regulator under section 91 of the 1984 Act apply in relation to the work to the higher-risk building (but not in relation to any other work specified in the initial notice).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The provisions of paragraph 5(4) to (9) also apply but as if any reference to the cancellation date were a reference to 6th April 2024.\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["From April 2024: cases where work has sufficiently progressed and then initial notice ceases"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-11"}], ["11."]}, "—(1) This paragraph applies where—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-11-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["paragraph 1 applies in relation to a particular building in respect of work for which an initial notice was in force on 6th April 2024;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-11-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["a notice under paragraph 1(4) (notice that work had sufficiently progressed) in relation to that work was received by a local authority before 6th April 2024;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-11-1-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["the initial notice for the work, or such part of the notice which relates to the higher-risk building, ceases to be in force by virtue of any provision of Part 2 of the 1984 Act on a date after 6th April 2024 (“the cancellation date”)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Where this paragraph applies—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-11-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if a final certificate relating to the work (or any part of the work which relates to the higher-risk building) has been accepted before the cancellation date then with effect from the notice date the function of enforcing building regulations that is conferred on the regulator by section 91(3) of the 1984 Act is not exercisable in relation to that work;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-11-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["if a plans certificate relating to the work (or any part of the work which relates to the higher-risk building) has been accepted before the cancellation date then with effect from the notice date the certificate ceases to have effect;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-11-2-c"}], ["(c)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["accordingly Parts 2 to 6 of these Regulations apply to the work from the cancellation date with the modifications provided for in paragraph 5(9) (as applied by paragraph (4));"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-11-2-d"}], ["(d)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["subject to paragraph (e), the 2010 Regulations, to the extent they apply to higher-risk buildings, apply to any of the work from that date;"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-11-2-e"}], ["(e)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["regulation 11(3) of the 2010 Regulations does not apply and accordingly the regulator may exercise the power in section 8(3A) of the 1984 Act to dispense with or relax any requirement of the 2010 Regulations."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Where this paragraph applies, with effect from the cancellation date the regulator, and not the local authority for the area, is the building control authority in relation to the higher-risk building and accordingly the duties and functions of the regulator under section 91 of the 1984 Act apply in relation to the work to the higher-risk building (but not in relation to any other work specified in the initial notice).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(4) The provisions of paragraph 5(4) to (9) also apply.\r"]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "schedule-3-part-2"}], []}, {"div", [{"class", "LegClearPart"}], []}, {"h3", [{"class", "LegPart"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegPartNo"}], ["PART 2"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegPartTitle"}], ["Enforcement and interpretation"]}]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitleFirst"}], ["Contravention of certain provisions not to be an offence etc"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-12"}], ["12."]}, "—(1) The following provisions of this Schedule are prescribed for the purposes of section 35(2) of the 1984 Act as provisions in relation to which section 35(1) does not apply—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-12-1-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["paragraphs 4(4) and 5(4) (including as applied by paragraphs 15(4) and 16(4)) (duties of approved inspectors);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-12-1-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["paragraph 6 (from April 2024: local authority to notify regulator where work has not sufficiently progressed)."]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) The following provisions of this Schedule are prescribed for the purposes of section 35B(7)(a) of the 1984 Act as provisions in relation to which a compliance notice(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00044"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 44"}, {"id", "Backf00044"}], ["44"]}, ") may not be given—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-12-2-a"}], ["(a)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["paragraphs 4(4) and 5(4) (including as applied by paragraphs 15(4) and 16(4)) (duties of approved inspectors);"]}, "\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegP3Container"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegLHS LegP3No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-12-2-b"}], ["(b)"]}, {"span", [{"class", "LegDS LegRHS LegP3Text"}], ["paragraph 6 (from April 2024: local authority to notify regulator where work has not sufficiently progressed)."]}, "\r"]}, {"h4", [{"class", "LegP1GroupTitle"}], ["Interpretation"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP1ParaText"}], [{"span", [{"class", "LegP1No"}, {"id", "schedule-3-paragraph-13"}], ["13."]}, "—(1) For the purposes of this Schedule—\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“initial notice” is a notice given under section 47 of the 1984 Act;\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegListTextStandard LegLevel3"}], ["“", {"span", [{"class", "LegTerm"}, {"id", "term-full-plans"}], ["full plans"]}, "” means plans deposited with a local authority for the purposes of section 16 of the 1984 Act in accordance with regulations 12(2)(b) and 14 of the 2010 Regulations (as those provisions had effect immediately before 1st October 2023).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(2) Subject to sub-paragraph (3), any reference to work to which an initial notice relates is to be construed as a reference to that work as varied by an amendment notice given under section 51A of the 1984 Act(", {"a", [{"class", "LegFootnoteRef"}, {"href", "#f00045"}, {"title", "Go to footnote 45"}, {"id", "Backf00045"}], ["45"]}, ") which has been accepted.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegP2ParaText"}], ["(3) Sub-paragraph (2) does not apply where the amendment notice under section 51A of the 1984 Act is given on or after 1st October 2023 and is such that the work as varied becomes higher-risk building work.\r"]}, {"a", [{"class", "LegAnchorID"}, {"id", "Legislation-ExNote"}], []}, {"h2", [{"class", "LegExpNoteTitle"}], ["EXPLANATORY NOTE"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegCommentText"}], ["(This note is not part of the Regulations)\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["This instrument is part of a number of Regulations which implement Part 3 of the Building Safety Act ", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2022/30"}], ["2022 (c. 30)"]}, ".\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["Section 91ZA of the Building Act 1984 (as inserted by section 32 of the Building Safety Act 2022, which is to come into force on 1st October 2023, provides for the regulator to be the building control authority in relation to any higher-risk building in England and any proposed higher-risk building.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["The requirements in the Building Regulations 2010 continue to apply to higher-risk buildings. Amendments (to be made elsewhere) to those Regulations disapply most of the procedural requirements in those Regulations, consequently procedures in this instrument apply instead.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["Part 2 of these Regulations sets out the procedures for applying for building control approval in relation to higher-risk buildings. Applications must be submitted to the regulator giving the information required and accompanied by the plans and documents required. Building control approval may, with the applicant’s consent, be subject to a requirement, for example, to not progress beyond a specified point without agreement of the regulator or that more detailed plans or documents could be approved by the regulator at a later date.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["Part 3 of these Regulations sets out the change control process where any document relating to the work which was approved by the regulator at the application stage (or subsequently under a requirement or a change control) is to be changed. And provision is also made in this Part for change to the client, principal contractor or principal designer, insolvency etc of a client and variation of a requirement imposed on a building control approval.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["Part 4 of these Regulations sets out provisions in relation the golden thread information, mandatory occurrence reporting and the handover of information on completion of the work.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["Part 5 of these Regulations sets out the procedures for applying for a completion certificate in relation to higher-risk buildings. Applications must be submitted to the regulator giving the information required and accompanied by the plans and documents required. Provision is also made for partial completion certificates where it is proposed a building (or part of a building) is occupied before all of the higher-risk building work is completed.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["Part 6 of these Regulations sets out provision relating to inspections, testing and sampling, regularisation of unauthorised work, review by the regulator of its decisions, and appeals in relation to reviewed decisions and the procedure under section 30A of the Building Act 1984 (which provides that a request can be made to the Secretary of State for determination of an application where the regulator has not made a decision within the time limit prescribed).\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["Part 7 of these Regulations defines exempt work, gives the regulator the power by direction to require an application to be sent to it via a specified method, and also sets out those provisions in relation to which a stop notice under section 35C of that Act may be given. Part 7 also includes consequential amendments to the Regulatory Reform (Fire Safety) Order 2005 (", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2005/1541"}], ["S.I. 2005/1541"]}, "); the Community Infrastructure Levy Regulations 2010 (", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2010/948"}], ["S.I. 2010/948"]}, "); and the Building Safety (Responsible Actors Scheme and Prohibitions) Regulations 2023 (", {"a", [{"class", "LegCitation"}, {"title", "Go to item of legislation"}, {"rel", "cite"}, {"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2023/753"}], ["S.I. 2023/753"]}, "). Schedule 3 to these Regulations sets out transitional, supplementary and saving provisions in relation to projects for higher-risk building work for which plans were deposited or initial notices given before 1st October 2023.\r"]}, {"p", [{"class", "LegExpNoteText"}], ["A full impact assessment of the effect that this instrument will have on the costs to business is published with an Explanatory Memorandum alongside the instrument on ", {"a", [{"href", "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/"}, {"title", "UK Legislation"}], ["www.legislation.gov.uk"]}, ".\r"]}, {"div", [{"class", "LegFootnotes"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegFootnotesContainer"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegClearFix LegFootnote"}, {"id", "f00001"}], [{"div", [{"class", "LegFootnoteNoContainer"}], ["(", {"span", [{"class", "LegFootnoteNo"}], ["1"]}, ")"]}, 